text: Elisabet Ehrnrooth (born 2 May 1967) is a Finnish equestrian. She competed in the individual dressage event at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Finland Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:People from Nyköping Municipality
